:+- Select current line
:+ Next line
:- Prev line
:., Select des de cursor a final
:,. Select des de cursor a inici
Edit -+ s/^/	/ Tab current line
Edit -+ s/^	//
|a+
Edit s/^/	/g Tab
Edit s/^	//g Untab
Edit s/^	/    /g tabs2spaces
Edit s/^    /	/g spaces2tabs

Edit , s/\.html//g
